details.name: Admiral Torsten
details.text: I have a bad feeling about the road ahead. I need a scout here!

details.name: Scout
details.text: Let me be your eyes, Sir.

details.name: Scout
details.text: Bad news! The road is heavily fortified. They are anticipating us.

details.name: Scout
details.text: It's hard to tell, but I'm seeing something on the radar further down that path. I think the main base is even more guarded.

details.name: Scout
details.text: I'm getting some readings from the mountain valley to the west, but can't see anything there.

details.name: Admiral Torsten
details.text: With no more bridges to blow up, Grim resorted to a wall of armoured units. What is the status of our camp?

details.name: Infantry
details.text: Almost done, Sir. The only problem is that most of the radar systems for the Towers arrived damaged. We managed to restore one to a working condition, so we have comms.

details.name: Admiral Torsten
details.text: Damaged radars? What happened?

details.name: Infantry
details.text: The equipment looks smashed, we suspect it was sabotage.

details.name: Admiral Torsten
details.text: Someone sneaked up on us? Very worrying. We have to investigate this once we are done with Grim's roadblock. There are a few abandoned Amber Towers here, we have to capture tham ASAP.
Claim all Amber Noon buildings.
Admiral Torsten must survive

details.name: Amber Commander
details.text: Damn those Jade invaders! Requesting assistance!

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Finally! I was getting bored sitting in this valley.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Engineering corps, move in!

details.name: Engineer
details.text: Rapid deployment done!

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Clear out the trees!

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: All units, assault Jade Twilight positions!

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Tell me, Admiral, have your radar equipment arrived yet?

details.name: Admiral Torsten
details.text: I should have known it was you. It was a smart move, I must admit. Who told you to do that? Because I doubt you came up with this on your own.

details.name: Commando Blake
details.text: Laugh while you still can!
Claim all Amber Noon and Sapphire Dawn buildings.

details.name: Admiral Torsten
details.text: I admire Grim's persistence, but this is not going to be enough to stop me.

details.name: Admiral Torsten
details.text: It is worrysome to see Sapphire Dawn still dealing with that traitor. I can only hope, that President Gideon will see that soon.

details.name: Admiral Torsten
details.text: I overestimated my abilities here.
